snippet: Chella Choi shrugged off two bogeys to start the back nine, birdieing three late holes for a four-under 67 and a one-shot lead after the second round of the Jamie Farr Toledo Classic in Sylvania, Ohio.

headline.main: Choi Up by One at Jamie Farr Classic
